# Gráficos

```{r, echo=FALSE, fig.width=6, fig.height=6}
data(mpg)
ggplot(mpg, aes(x=displ, y = hwy, color = class)) + 
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal()
```

```{r, echo=FALSE, fig.width=ancho, fig.height=largo, out.width="70%", fig.align='center', fig.cap="Gráfico de ejemplo"}
data(mpg)
ggplot(mpg, aes(x=displ, y = hwy, color = class)) + 
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal()
```

